(defvar fnexpand-expand-env-directories  nil
  "If nono-nil then environment varaiables $DIR which contain
directory slash are expanded.

Examples; when nil, suppose PROJECT holds directory

  $PROJ[TAB] --> $PROJECT
  $PRIN[TAB] --> $PRINTER

When non-nil

